        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> Playing a dark elf necro. Untwinked so I can learn the class a bit before I dress him around 20. But anyway, any advice with spells or best ways to kill mobs, or how to keep your pet from KSing you would be appreciated. I have played a few int casters before but never past 9 or 10, so go easy on the lingo please. Am usually just a dumb melee, well hybrid actually but anywho</P><P> </font></td>

